'''加州州立大學弗雷斯諾分校'''（'''California State University, Fresno'''，常稱：'''Fresno State'''）是[[加利福尼亞州立大學|加利福尼亞州立大學]]系統內、位於美國加利福尼亞州[[弗雷斯諾|弗雷斯諾]]的一所公立大學，成立於1911年。<ref name="forbes.com">{{Cite web |url=http://www.forbes.com/top-colleges/list/ |title=America's Top Colleges List<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2015-02-19 |archive-date=2018-01-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180115001503/https://www.forbes.com/top-colleges/list/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> 這座大學所在的城市位於[[內華達山脈_(美國)|內華達山脈]]山腳，該城則為加州第五大城市。2015年在《[[美國新聞與世界報道|美國新聞與世界報道]]》“西部地區大學排名”中排在第46位。<ref>{{cite web|title=California State University, Fresno|url=http://colleges.usnews.rankingsandreviews.com/best-colleges/csu-fresno-1147|publisher=U.S. News and World Report|accessdate=2015-02-18|archive-date=2015-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150215122317/http://colleges.usnews.rankingsandreviews.com/best-colleges/csu-fresno-1147|dead-url=no}}</ref>

大學校園裡有一座天文館和葡萄園，還擁有一座商用釀酒廠，其中的酒由學生來釀製。<ref>{{cite journal|title=Fresno State wines win record 49 medals|journal=Western Farm Press|date=September 8, 2009|url=http://westernfarmpress.com/grapes/fresno-state-wines-win-record-49-medals|access-date=2015-02-19|archive-date=2015-02-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150219185615/http://westernfarmpress.com/grapes/fresno-state-wines-win-record-49-medals|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Pride Points, Unique Facilities, Hands-on|url=http://www.fresnostate.edu/jcast/ve/about-us/pride-points.html|work=Fresno State website|publisher=California State University, Fresno|accessdate=25 April 2014|archive-date=2015-02-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150219195049/http://www.fresnostate.edu/jcast/ve/about-us/pride-points.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 其圖書館為加州州立大學系統中23所分校里的第三大圖書館。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.calstate.edu/library/content/statistics/ |title=Systemwide Digital Library Content | Academic Technology Services | CSU |publisher=Calstate.edu |date= |accessdate=2014-08-18 |archive-date=2014-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141108075156/http://www.calstate.edu/library/content/statistics/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

